'''''Lithilaria''''' is a [[genus]] of [[moth]]s of the [[Noctuidae]] family.

==Selected Species==
*''[[Lithilaria anomozancla]]'' <small>(Turner, 1944)</small> 
*''[[Lithilaria melanostrotum]]'' <small>(Turner, 1906)</small> 
*''[[Lithilaria ossicolor]]'' <small>Rosenstock, 1885</small> 
*''[[Lithilaria proestans]]'' <small>(T.P. Lucas, 1895)</small> 

